      "text": "OHSHIMA, Yoshiki, LUNZER, Aran, EVANS, Jenn, FREUDENBERG, Vanessa, UPTON, Brian and SMITH, David A., 2022. An Experiment in Live Collaborative Programming on the Croquet Shared Experience Platform. In: Companion Proceedings of the 6th International Conference on the Art, Science, and Engineering of Programming. Online. New York, NY, USA: Association for Computing Machinery. 8 December 2022. p. 46–53. [Accessed 28 April 2023]. Programming ’22. ISBN 978-1-4503-9656-1. DOI 10.1145/3532512.3535224. [https://tinlizzie.org/IADocs/live-programming-greenlight.pdf pdf]"
